d mfp_mfx. Marginal effects after mfp using f_able.
d
d mfp_mfx calculates marginal effects for non-linear models 
d fitted using the mfp command. 
d
d REQUIREMENT: This package requires the user-written 
d package f_able (findit f_able) to function.
d
d Author: Dr Chao Wang
d Associate Professor in Health & Social Care Statistics
d Kingston University
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260309
